{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"eaa50a71fb","title":"给毛宇居、文梅清、张有成的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1418e001e6","index":0,"year":1951,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"eaa50a71fb"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"25bd4586c2","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"eaa50a71fb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张有成（1886-1953），湖南省韶山市大坪乡新联村人，木工。毛泽东少年时的朋友。大革命时期曾参加韶山农民运动。"}],"contents":[{"id":"71ef802131","type":"title","text":"给毛宇居、文梅清、张有成的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"eaa50a71fb"},{"id":"25bd4586c2","type":"paragraph","text":"禹居、梅清、有成三兄","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"eaa50a71fb"},{"id":"34c79b2665","type":"paragraph","text":"接到梅清、有成二兄的信，想来京一游，我认为可行。如禹居兄有兴趣，亦可同来一游。来者以三兄为限，他人不要来。到京大约可住一个月至两个月，太久则不方便。如三兄同意这几点，即可借我这里派的同志一道来京。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"eaa50a71fb"},{"id":"3b370bfca4","type":"paragraph","text":"此祝健吉！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"eaa50a71fb"},{"id":"2236fd8ff3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"eaa50a71fb"},{"id":"223434ca5d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年九月四日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"eaa50a71fb"}],"page":{"id":"806687a078","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"eaa50a71fb","start":482,"end":482}}}},"__N_SSG":true}